high_descs: Turn around and hang a left midway beyond the black table to face the dining table.
Pick up the white plate on the left side of the table to the right of the statue.
Turn left, hang a right at the trash can and turn right just beyond the black couch to face the glass coffee table.
Place the white plate on the bottom shelf of the coffee table.
Turn around, hang a left at the trash can and walk to the dining table on your left.
Pick up the white plate closest to the edge of the dining table.
Turn left, hang a right at the trash can and turn right just beyond the black couch to face the glass coffee table.
Place the white plate on top of the coffee table in the back left corner.
anns.task_desc: Place two plates on a coffee table.

high_descs: Turn right, move to the table, to the place setting near the statue.
Pick up the plate on the left.
Turn left, move to the coffee table.
Place the plate on the lower shelf of the coffee table.
Turn left, move to the table, to the place setting near the statue.
Pick up the plate closest to the edge.
Turn left, move to the coffee table.
Place the plate on the top of the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Place two plates on to the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn right and go between the dining table and the black console table, then turn left to face the dining table.
Pick up the leftmost white plate from the table.
Bring the plate with you and cross the room, then face the glass coffee table in front of the sofa.
Put the plate down on the bottom platform of the coffee table.
Go back to the same spot at the dining table and turn left to face it again.
Pick up the white plate closest to the table's edge.
Bring the plate with you and move back to the glass coffee table.
Put the plate down on the top part of the table in the center.
anns.task_desc: Move some plates to the coffee table.
